<http://www.spektrix.com/yukonartscentre/event/68601AQKLCDVNPLVQHKNKQBDVTKMGMSJQ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Annie JR.";
  schema:description """
	<h2>Art From the Heart 2026 Presents: ANNIE JR.</h2><span><br/></span>The Heart of Riverdale’s musical theatre class has been working all year to prepare Annie JR. for you. Under the direction of Artistic Director Michelle FisherMayr, this story is a treasured classic. With equal measures of pluck and positivity, little orphan Annie charms everyone's hearts despite a next-to-nothing start in 1930s New York City. Annie is determined to find the parents who abandoned her years ago on the doorstep of an orphanage run by the cruel Miss Hannigan. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Art From the Heart 2026, Presented by Gilday Holdings Ltd, Quantum Machine Works Ltd. and Streamline Architects.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This year’s Art From the Heart is made-up of four different performances: <span><br/></span>Dance of the Coralines (an original piece by our Pre Professionals, including Beat Street 4, 5)<span><br/></span>A Ballet Fiesta (all Ballet)<span><br/></span>I Love You So Munsch (Recreational and After School Crews 1,2&3 levels)<span><br/></span>Annie JR.(Musical Theatre and Classical Squad 4, 5).<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please ensure your tickets correspond to the shows you are intending on seeing!<span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-05-29T19:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
