<http://www.spektrix.com/yukonartscentre/event/68801ALBSQSHRCDRCGNPHHPCVVCPMPMDD>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "I Love You So Munsch";
  schema:description """
	<h2>Art From the Heart 2026 Presents: I Love You So Munsch</h2><span><br/></span>Join The Heart’s recreational Saturday classes, as well as our young after school crews, as they weave together the familiar and beloved stories of Robert Munsch through dance. The Heart of Riverdale’s preschoolers, our Heart Heroes, have narrated the audio for this performance.  The show will culminate with some pieces presented by our pre professionals from their show Dance of the Coralines.  A great way to spend an afternoon in May!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Art From the Heart 2026, Presented by Gilday Holdings Ltd, Quantum Machine Works Ltd. and Streamline Architects.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This year’s Art From the Heart is made-up of four different performances: <span><br/></span>Dance of the Coralines (an original piece by our Pre Professionals, including Beat Street 4, 5)<span><br/></span>A Ballet Fiesta (all Ballet)<span><br/></span>I Love You So Munsch (Recreational and After School Crews 1,2&3 levels)<span><br/></span>Annie JR.(Musical Theatre and Classical Squad 4, 5).<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please ensure your tickets correspond to the shows you are intending on seeing!<span><br/></span>
""";
